  <prompt>
    Build two new Custom Pages: `sprk_kpiassessmentspage.html` and `sprk_invoicespage.html` — each ~50 lines following the ADR-026 standard (Vite + vite-plugin-singlefile + React 19). Each mounts `<FluentProvider applyStylesToPortals theme={...}>` wrapping `<DataGrid configId={...} parentContext={fromUrlParams}/>`. Parses URL params `entityName / filterField / filterValue` for Matter-context filter. For the Invoice page, register the Mark Paid custom command handler if UQ-05 was R1.
  </prompt>

  <role>
    SPAARKE platform developer. Expert in ADR-026 Custom Page standard, Vite singlefile bundling, React 19 + Fluent v9 + applyStylesToPortals.
  </role>

  <goal>
    Two Custom Page web resources (single-file HTML bundles) deploy to Dataverse; both open correctly in dialog + standalone modes with Matter context filter applied; both register correct handlers; ~50 lines of TypeScript each (excluding boilerplate).
  </goal>

  <context>
    <background>
      Per FR-CON-03 + FR-CON-04 + NFR-11. The Custom Page shell pattern is ~50 lines: parse URL params, build `parentContext`, mount FluentProvider + DataGrid. Reuses task 021/022 configIds. For Invoice page: if UQ-05 is R1, register the Mark Paid handler via `registerCommandHandler`. Either page can default `dataverseClient` to `XrmDataverseClient` (host is MDA Custom Page).
    </background>
    <relevant-files>
      <file>src/solutions/sprk_kpiassessmentspage/src/main.tsx</file>
      <file>src/solutions/sprk_kpiassessmentspage/vite.config.ts</file>
