  <steps>
    <step order="1">Run `/fluent-v9-component` skill Step 0.5 checklist.</step>
    <step order="2">Scaffold `src/solutions/sprk_kpiassessmentspage/` per ADR-026 pattern: Vite config, package.json, index.html, src/main.tsx (~50 lines).</step>
    <step order="3">In `main.tsx`: parse URL params (`entityName / filterField / filterValue / matterId`); build `parentContext = { matterId }`; mount `<FluentProvider applyStylesToPortals theme={webLightTheme}>` wrapping `<DataGrid configId="<from task 021>" parentContext={parentContext}/>`.</step>
    <step order="4">Same pattern for `sprk_invoicespage/`. If UQ-05 is R1, additionally register Mark Paid handler via `registerCommandHandler("mark-paid", handler)`.</step>
    <step order="5">Run `npm run build` in each — verify single-file HTML output is generated.</step>
    <step order="6">Smoke test locally via Vite dev server (`npm run dev`).</step>
    <step order="7">Local Storybook story or harness: pass mock URL params + verify renders correctly with mock data.</step>
    <step order="8">Update TASK-INDEX (023 ✅).</step>
    <step order="9">Document any deviations.</step>
  </steps>

  <tools>
    <tool name="npm">Build + Vite</tool>
    <tool name="Edit">Author shell files</tool>
  </tools>

